This package is an original, clean-room Swift implementation that reads and writes
ARINC 633-4–conformant XML. It does NOT include, redistribute, or reproduce ARINC
Specification 633 or its XSD schemas, which are copyrighted by AEEC / SAE-ITC. Users are
assumed to hold their own license to the specification. All bundled test fixtures are
synthetic and contain no real operational or crew data.

This product depends on ZIPFoundation (https://github.com/weichsel/ZIPFoundation),
licensed under the MIT License, used only for the double-zipped EFF container.
